MockEndpoint mock = getMockEndpoint("mock:result").     mock.expectedMinimumMessageCount(1).     assertMockEndpointsSatisfied(100L, TimeUnit.SECONDS). Object body = exchange.getIn().getBody().     assertNotNull(header).     assertNotNull(body). }
